(Terrible Tianhai Sect, terrible Bobo!)

4
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:02,799
I'm getting water.

5
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,079
Write two sheets.

6
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,959
Don't cheat.

7
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:06,919
Okay.

8
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,360
Young man.

9
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:24,879
How are you?

10
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,639
Are you getting used to being here?

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,879
It's okay.

12
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,719
Can you drink?

13
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,800
A little.

14
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:48,000
Thank you for taking care of Ming.

15
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,439
We take care of each other.

16
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,759
Hui said you're not bad.

17
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,960
Really?

18
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,240
So you're complimenting me.

19
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:03,319
Qi said you're a radish.

20
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,280
Radish?

21
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:07,000
Playboy.

22
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,840
How am I a playboy?

23
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:12,960
Being outside,

24
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,800
you should know your limits.

25
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,719
Got it?

26
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,680
Back in the day,

27
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,080
I also ran the streets.

28
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:23,840
In just a few years,
someone called me Boss.

29
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,840
Then the crackdown came.

30
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:27,560
There's no way.

31
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:30,240
Our boss said I have made a name

32
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,319
and profits too.

33
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,919
I should retire.

34
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,800
At that time, I was at my peak.

35
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,919
No way!

36
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,759
As a result...

37
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:37,879
Then what?

38
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,680
I regret it till now.

39
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,000
What I regret is not important.

40
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,639
What's important is you.

41
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,680
Mr. Luo,

42
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,280
thank you for telling me this.

43
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,240
I'm quite touched.

44
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,360
However,

45
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,960
I'm unfamiliar with my surroundings.

46
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,319
I've only half-stepped in.

47
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,800
Young man,

48
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,479
I've seen a lot of people.

49
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,439
You're not suited for this life.

50
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,519
Are you praising me or criticizing me?

51
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,120
When you're free,

52
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,639
come here.

53
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:22,040
Stay away from that shady business.

54
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,880
Understood?

55
00:04:26,679 --> 00:04:27,519
Why haven't you

56
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,000
come for dinner recently?

57
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,279
I don't mind imposing.

58
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:35,480
But I also have limits.

59
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,160
I can't mooch meals every day.

60
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,079
How inappropriate.

61
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,159
Inappropriate?

62
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,440
Is it appropriate?

63
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,960
Okay.

64
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:45,399
Then I'll go when I have time.

65
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,439
Tell Ming about

66
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,240
what we're talking today.

67
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,279
Don't tell him I said it.

68
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,159
Got it?

69
00:04:59,599 --> 00:05:00,439
Also,

70
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,680
don't let Qi know

71
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,720
I'm drinking here.

72
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,759
My name

73
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:24,279
gets you served.

74
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,839
How can I be so bold?

75
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,000
Don't be shy.

76
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,200
Okay.

77
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,639
Come by for dinner anytime.

78
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,320
Wait!

79
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,480
Did you sneak out to drink again?

80
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,480
(Because I know)

81
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,480
(that with you there,)

82
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:26,720
whether it's Lian'an Town

83
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,680
or anywhere else,

84
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,880
